data.description: ACTIVE UNDER CONTRACT- ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS. Ready to have your Breath Taken Away at this Beauty of a Home? Welcome Home to the Villages of GlenLakes in this 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Maintenance Free Villa Home boasting an Updated Kitchen with all new high-end appliances that sits perfectly right next to your newly renovated Pool! As you pull up in you brand new paver driveway, you will see Perfection in Landscaping. Entering this Amazing Home, you will see beautiful new floors flowing throughout this open concept home. Check out your second bedroom that has become its own private suite with its custom-made Barn Door!! As you enter this family & Living room one can look out to the Triple Door Entry Way that fully opens up into your Gorgeous Florida Room with all the Extras! Check out the Chef's Kitchen with lots of prepping space for the Chef or Wanna-Be Chef and great areas to entertain your family & friends. Kitchen stove is incredibly unique.... It is an Advantium Oven Convection/Microwave/Speed Heat Oven with Infra-Red and Stove has Built In Air Fryer. Check out the oversized Fridge with lots of customized features & Upgrades. This seller missed nothing in detail when they added all the distinctive features in this home. Wait till you see the Garage.... Check out the RACE DECK Flooring throughout Garage & Workshop area. Enjoy shelving and a workbench for the hobbyist, Car Enthusiasts and more including and additional 30 Amp Plug Set-Up for those who need an Electric Car Charger Hookup. You will always be Organized with this garage's shelving & storage. Inside Laundry and new floors throughout welcome you into your Master Suite!! A Paradise like no other. This Master Suite is Oversized and leads into your Brand New 4 Piece EnSuite with Walk In Shower, Relaxing Huge Garden Tub, Dual Sinks and so much more. Enjoy walk-in closets and plenty of storage throughout this home. The Florida Room/Back Porch area was customed designed for the homeowner who likes to relax, stretch out, entertain, enjoy a beverage watching sunrises & sunsets. Fully carpeted with outdoor carpet, private and back door exit makes this the ideal porch for the Florida Homeowner. This home has a New Tile Roof in 2021, New Hot Water Heater, Newer AC Unit serviced yearly and new Garage Tracks for smooth operations. This homeowner spared no expense when they put the best of everything into this home. Enjoy the Good Life in Glen Lakes with a stunning Golf Course, Golf Cart Friendly Lifestyle, miles of trails & natural preserves for walking & hiking to an Amazing Clubhouse with Country Club Style Restaurant & Bar overlooking your Olympic Size pool, Tennis Courts, Pickleball Courts and more. GlenLakes has been named a 'Top 50 Community' by Where to Retire and Ideal-Living magazines with over 100 different Clubs you can be a part of. Enjoy maintenance free living and security in this Gated Community with incredible lakes & landscaping throughout your community. Only moments to Weeki Wachee Springs, Buccaneer Bay, Pine Island, Hernando Beach, Crystal River & Homosassa and more, GlenLakes is perfectly situated to enjoy Kayaking, Canoeing, Boating, Paddleboarding and more in the Fresh Springs, Brackish & Salt waters while moments from great hiking natural preserves. Less than 10 minutes from Top Hospitals & Medical facilities, GlenLakes is right by the Best Restaurants, Shopping, Wineries/Breweries and so much more. Hurry to see this home for it will not Last.
